1. *Veka* je prošla, a nisu svi svoje obaveze ispunili. (The era has passed and not everyone fulfilled their obligations.)

2. Svi su se trudili da unaprede život u novoj *veci*. (Everyone tried to improve life in the new era.)

3. U poslednjem *veku* postojale su mnoge inovacije. (In the last century there were many innovations.)

4. U prošlim *vekovima* bilo je slabijih tehnoloških mogućnosti. (In past centuries there were weaker technological possibilities.)

5. U ovom *veku* postoje snažne računarske infrastrukture. (In this century there are strong computing infrastructures.)